data.description: Looking for a handyman special?  This is a great opportunity in the Mini Farms for an 1836 sqft, 3 bedrooms, 3 bath, Homes of Merit double wide on 5.23 acres.  Not in a flood zone, no wetlands, no deed restrictions and an HOA for road maintenance only.  Needs some work, TLC and cleanup.  New roof 2016.  Located between Crystal River and Dunnellon with access to everything the Nature Coast has to offer.
